pageContext.claim: “[Obama] wouldn't endorse [Biden]. He was a vice president and wouldn't endorse him, made all these terrible statements, wouldn't endorse him, and then even after he won, it was months before he endorsed him because he didn't want to see it happen.I think he's probably the most surprised person on Earth, Obama.”
pageContext.analysis: Obama, as a former Democratic president, stayed neutral until the party's primary process was completed. He did not refuse to endorse Biden.
